data.description: Have a love of the water? Make this stately 2 family home located in the heart of Arverne by the Bay yours. The first floor apartment has a private entrance and features 2 bedrooms and 1 full bathroom. The owners unit is spread over 2 floors and has 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. This home features hardwood floors and tiled kitchen and baths. Additional storage is available on the first floor and in attic. Private parking for 2-3 cars, a deck and backyard complete this package. Located in one of Rockaways hottest up and coming communities, close to new restaurants, bars, breweries, shops, the beach, boardwalk, boat yards and public transportation to NYC. Just 25 minutes to JFK International airport.
